reviewText: I loved and enjoyed this movie it was a lil pricy but worth seeing as I couldn't find it no where else!!!
Yuck!  Sickening stupid movie.  No wonder I couldn't find it on DVD.  Swimming in poop - some on - while wearing scuba gear.  Who wrote that?  Geez!!!!!!
This is Gloria Trevi's best movie without a doubt. i hope that one day this one will also make it's DVD release just like the last 2. it would be a dream come true.
